                            target="_blank">Crystal
							Gateway Marriott</a> are available for attendees of the Global Methane, Climate and
						Clean Air Forum. The Marriott will offer rooms at the federal per diem rate of $257 per night
						(plus
						applicable state and local taxes) for rooms booked by <strong>Sunday, 11 September
							2022</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        To make a reservation, use our <a href="https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=1656648627937&key=GRP&app=resvlink" target="_blank">room block link</a> or call Marriott Reservations at
