                    </p>
                    <h3 id="gettinghere">Getting to the Marriott</h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>From the Ronald Reagan Washington International Airport (DCA)</strong>. The Crystal
						Gateway
						Marriott is
						conveniently located 2 miles from the airport. There are multiple ways to get to the hotel:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Complimentary Hotel Shuttle</strong>. The hotel provides a complimentary shuttle
							from
							the airport that
							runs from 5:00 am to 11:30 pm ET daily. The shuttle picks up from Terminal 2 on the Baggage
							Claim
							(Arrivals) Level – 1st floor. <a
                                href="https://www.flyreagan.com/parking-transportation/ground-transportation"
                                target="_blank">DCA Ground Transportation Details</a>.</li>
                        <li><strong>Metro</strong>. The hotel is also accessible by the DC Metro
							Yellow
							and Blue lines.
							Follow the signs at DCA for the Metro and board the Blue Line towards Largo Town Center or
							the
							Yellow Line towards Fort Totten/Greenbelt. The Crystal City Metro station is only one stop away from
							DCA. Once you exit the Metro at Crystal City, follow the signs for the Crystal Gateway
							Marriott.

                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Taxi or Rideshare</strong>.You may get to and from the airport using a taxi or a Rideshare app such as Uber, Lyft, or ALTO. Green flags located outside on the outer terminal curb designate the appropriate pick-up loading zones. </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        <strong>From Dulles International Airport (IAD) or Baltimore-Washington Thurgood Marshall
							International Airport (BWI).</strong>
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Ground Transportion Details.</strong> Details are available for <a href="https://www.flydulles.com/parking-transportation/ground-transportation" target="_blank">Dulles International</a> and <a href="https://www.bwiairport.com/to-from-bwi/transportation" target="_blank">BWI</a>.</li>
                        <li><strong>Taxi or Rideshare.</strong> Taxis are readily available or you may use a Rideshare app such as Uber, Lyft, or ALTO. </li>
                    </ul>
                    <h3 id="parking">Parking</h3>
                    <p>Parking is available at the hotel at a discounted rate of $25 per day.</p>
                    <h3 id="whattopack">What to Pack</h3>
                    <p>
                        Dress is business casual for local weather. Average temperatures for the end of September range
						from
						70°F to 80°F (21°C to 27°C). <a
                            href="https://www.accuweather.com/en/us/arlington/22201/weather-forecast/331250"
                            target="_blank">Check local
							weather</a>.
                    </p>
                    <h3 id="thingstodo">Things to Do</h3>
                    <p>
                        The Crystal Gateway Marriott is conveniently located between the Crystal City and Pentagon City
						neighborhoods in Arlington, Virginia. Both Crystal City and Pentagon City offer plenty of
						options
						for restaurants, coffee shops, and local attractions. Washington, D.C. is also a quick Metro or
						car
						ride away.
                    </p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>The Crystal Gateway Marriott has a restaurant within the hotel that is open daily. <a
                            href="https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/wasgw-crystal-gateway-marriott/dining/"
                            target="_blank">View a
								list of nearby restaurants.</a></li>
                        <li>Dunkin’ (Coffee) – located underneath the Marriott, near the Metro entrance.</li>
                        <li>Starbucks (Coffee) – 8-minute walk from the Marriott at the corner of S Fern St. and 12th Street
							S.</li>
                        <li>CVS Pharmacy – 0.4 miles from the Marriott at 1550 Crystal Drive Suite C, Arlington, VA 22202.
                        </li>
                        <li>Harris Teeter (Grocery Store) – about a 1 mile, or 20-minute, walk from the hotel at 900
							Army
							Navy Dr, Arlington, VA 22202</li>
                    </ul>
